subproject.description:
(I) Strategic MoP Capacity Development Plan developed and endorsed to support the implementation of a Programme Based Approach at MoP;
(II) Local poverty/MDG monitoring tool developed; 
(III) Key policy documents widely disseminated at central and local levels;
(IV) Three year MoP/UNDP work-plan to support the implementation of the MPSP approved.

